        <head>Desert Heat</head>
        <lg Chorus="yes" number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Days are longer, nowhere, desert heat. </l>
          <l>Short with water, short with air to breath, </l>
          <l>I see boat by tears, but it isn't real. </l>
          <l>All my vision kills, all those fancy will </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>Days are longer, but I don't have much time to loose </l>
          <l>Hope that someday, we will find which way to choose </l>
          <l>Somewhere snowing, somewhere desert heat </l>
          <l>Far to notice, which star is yours to seek </l>
        </lg>
        <lg Chorus="yes" number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>Days are longer, nowhere, desert heat...</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
